83
84static const int _ctf_nerr = sizeof (_ctf_errlist) / sizeof (_ctf_errlist[0]);
85
86const char *
87ctf_errmsg(int error)
88{
89 const char *str;
90
91 if (error >= ECTF_BASE && (error - ECTF_BASE) < _ctf_nerr)
92 str = _ctf_errlist[error - ECTF_BASE];
93 else
94 str = ctf_strerror(error);
95
96 return (str ? str : "Unknown error");
97}
98
99int
100ctf_errno(ctf_file_t *fp)
101{
102 return (fp->ctf_errno);
103}
